                    <div class="col-md-6"><!-- right content col 6 -->
                        <div class="about-right-content"> <!-- right content wrapper -->
                            
                            <p>This website is all about visualizing the data from the survey conducted on caregivers of people effected with Alzheimer's disease to provide more better services by <strong>IPSCR</strong>. <strong>Alzheimer's is a type of dementia that causes problems with memory, thinking and behavior</strong>.</p> 

                            <p>There were several questionnaires made for the survey and the data collected from the survey is formatted into almost 40 files. These files are categorized into 3 catogeries that are listed below. This visualization website helps the surveyors in better understanding the information.  </p>

                            <p>Apart from visualizing the data , we also incorporate the resources that made this visualization possible through some static web-pages . We also attempted to incorporate some cool features in this visualization tool , so please go through the <strong>Tool usage </strong> section at the bottom of this website for better understanding.</p>

                            <p> Here is the webpage link from where we collected data to make this visualization possible . </p>
                            
                            <p class="center"><a  href="http://www.icpsr.umich.edu/icpsrweb/ICPSR/studies/03678" >ICPSR RESOURCES  </a></p>

                            
                            

                        </div><!-- end right content wrapper -->
                    </div><!-- end right content col 6 -->

